                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "好運劍"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成3點<span style=\"color: #FF9999\">火元素傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/292125737/7fae27e2ff070ba5aedf9d5c45e28d2e_8674385269545639539.png",
                "id": "talent74658",
                "key": "熱情超載",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "熱情超載"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>，生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">鼓舞領域</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">鼓舞領域</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">出戰狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">我方角色使用技能時：</span>如果該角色生命值至少爲7，則使此傷害額外+2；技能結算後，如果該角色生命值不多於6，則治愈該角色2點。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/292125737/bf3ffcaa5b9f41654043224fc74f3363_4915981396622915745.png",
                "id": "talent36637",
                "key": "美妙旅程",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "美妙旅程"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">融化</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">蒸發</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超載</span>：本傷害+2，目標強制切換到下一個角色</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/23/84496276/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_1478996059814332478.png",
                "id": "talent86940",
                "key": "火元素傷害·其一",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "火元素傷害·其一"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒</span>：本傷害+1，召喚<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒烈焰</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\"><br></span><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒烈焰</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結束階段：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：1，最多叠加到2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/23/84496276/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_3228580599966319769.png",
                "id": "talent13403",
                "key": "火元素傷害·其二",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/23/84496276/3c3362a64ac984342133762388c9eb41_4797691897135608494.png",
                "title": "火元素傷害·其二"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span></strong></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持續回合</span></strong></p><p>每回合結束階段，持續回合-1；</p><p>持續回合耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/23/84496276/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_8055478800869463979.png",
